title: Darrelle Revis dreaming of Super Bowl date after New York Jets win at ... - Sutton Guardian
text:
New York Jets cornerback Darrelle Revis is hoping a Wembley win can be the springboard his team needs to go on to the Super Bowl. The Jets beat the Miami Dolphins 27-14 in London on Sunday to improve to 3-1 as they immediately bounced back from last week's loss to the Philadelphia Eagles.
 Sutton Guardian.
